name: A Reflective Fantasy
description:
In terms of superficial achievements, the artist has made it.
Recognition achieved, money rolling in, love coming from all corners, yet one thing is missing: happiness.
It cannot be bought, nor drawn.
It must be figured out, and it starts from within.
The artist floats on an endless sea. It begins in silence. The feeling, the thinking.
Their shadow warps the water. A yellow light expands on the blue horizon.
They now have to learn how to swim there.
